original_conversation
Do you think that climate change is responsible for the recent floods ?
It could be . There are floods in this country almost every year , but in recent years they have been more widespread and more frequent .
It seems that the climate in this country is changing .
The summers are hotter . The last three summers have been the hottest for the past 200 years . There have also been stronger winds .
